#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:2
msgid "整板检测"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:6
msgid ""
"针对 PCB **整体表面** "
"的检测（不依赖具体元件）。常用于检测元件之间、丝印边缘等区域的污渍、异物、残留物等表面缺陷，作为对单元件检测的补充。整板检测的 ROI "
"不再以单个元件为单位，而是以 **包含 / 排除区域** 为单位划定。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:10
msgid "进入 **产品编程页面**（Teach），点击顶部标签页 **整板检测**。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:-1
msgid "整板检测主界面：左侧检测项列表 + 包含 / 排除区域工具 + 中央 PCB 画布"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:16
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:18
msgid "**1. 启用检测项**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:20
msgid "页面右侧提供检测项列表。当前支持的检测项："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:22
msgid ""
"**表面污染检测（Surface Contamination）**：基于 AI 模型，识别 PCB "
"表面的污渍、油渍、毛刺、异物等污染缺陷。每个检测项可独立启用 / 关闭。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:24
msgid "需要时勾选对应检测项的开关。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:26
msgid "**2. 绘制检测区域**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:28
msgid "整板检测使用两类区域定义有效检测范围："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:30
msgid "**包含区域（Include Regions，绿色）**：明确要检测的区域。若 **未定义任何包含区域**，系统默认将整块 PCB 作为检测范围。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:31
msgid ""
"**排除区域（Exclude "
"Regions，红色）**：在检测范围内主动排除的区域。常用于跳过治具边缘、丝印商标、二维码贴纸等不希望被误判为污渍的位置。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:33
msgid "在画布上点击工具栏对应按钮即可开始绘制："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:35
msgid "选中绿色 **添加包含区域** 按钮 → 在画布上拖动框选包含区域。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:36
msgid "选中红色 **添加排除区域** 按钮 → 在画布上拖动框选排除区域。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:38
msgid "每个区域绘制完成后会出现在右侧的 **区域列表** 中。点击列表项可："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:40
msgid "**定位（Locate）**：让相机移动到该区域，便于核对位置。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:41
msgid "**删除**：移除该区域。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:43
msgid "**3. 保存配置**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:45
msgid "所有改动会自动保存到当前产品的整板检测配置中，无需手动点击保存按钮。检测时系统会自动按当前配置执行。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:47
msgid "**表面污染检测（Surface Contamination）**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:49
msgid "表面污染检测以 AI 模型为核心。开启该检测项后："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:51
msgid "系统在每次检测时会对所有 **包含区域 - 排除区域** 内的像素做表面缺陷推理；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:52
msgid "AI 给出的污染区域会在复检页面上以高亮显示，便于人工确认；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:53
msgid "模型的可检范围会随产品配置与训练数据迭代而调整。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:55
msgid "**注意事项**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:59
msgid "**元件检测时表面泛红 — 占位元件 workaround：**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:61
msgid ""
"若某些倾斜元件在编程时显示正常（位于视野中部）、但在检测时表面被环形光源照得发红（位于视野边缘），可在该元件 "
"**周围添加一个更大的占位元件**\\ "
"（仅保留本体检测、阈值放到最宽松）。占位元件本身不会真正影响判定，但能改变智能路径规划，使原元件落在视野中部，避免边缘红光干扰。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/whole_board_inspection.rst:65
msgid ""
"整板检测与单元件检测 **同时启用、各自独立判定**。整板检测发现的污染区域不会改变单元件的 OK/NG 状态，但在复检页面上会与元件 NG "
"一并列出，便于操作员同时处理。"
msgstr ""

